OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783678767
OL,3,CMan banned from keeping animals after
OL,4,Che was filmed throwing dog over gate
OL,6,FWARNING: Contains details that some
OL,7,Fpeople might find distressing
OL,9,FA man has been banned from keeping
OL,10,Fanimals for ten years after an
OL,11,Funderweight dog was filmed being
OL,12,Fthrown over a six-foot-high garden
OL,13,Fgate in Bristol.
OL,15,FIn September 2025, James Marchant, 42,
OL,16,Fwas recorded by his neighbours
OL,17,Fgrabbing the terrier by the neck and
OL,18,Fthrowing it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
