PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783678767
OL,3,CMan banned from keeping animals after
OL,4,Che was filmed throwing dog over gate
OL,6,FThe neighbours who were filming
OL,7,FMarchant reported that he had wrestled
OL,8,Fthe dog, called Boomer, to the floor
OL,9,Fbefore picking it up.
OL,11,FThey shouted at him to stop and
OL,12,Fcontacted the police which led to his
OL,13,Farrest. The RSPCA brought a private
OL,14,Fprosecution through the court.
OL,16,FThe vet that viewed the footage told
OL,17,FBristol Magistrates' Court the dog,
OL,18,Fcalled Boomer, would have experienced
OL,19,Fpain and anxiety from the incident.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783678767
OL,3,CMan banned from keeping animals after
OL,4,Che was filmed throwing dog over gate
OL,6,FThe court also heard that Boomer was
OL,7,Funderweight and malnourished.
OL,9,FMarchant, of Privet Drive, Hartcliffe,
OL,10,FBristol, pleaded guilty to two animal
OL,11,Fwelfare offences, one concerning
OL,12,Fthrowing Boomer over the fence, and
OL,13,Fanother for failing to meet his need
OL,14,Ffor a suitable diet.
OL,16,FHe was banned from keeping animals for
OL,17,F10 years, ordered to pay #400 in costs
OL,18,Fand an #80 victim surcharge.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
