PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783678767
OL,3,CMan banned from keeping animals after
OL,4,Che was filmed throwing dog over gate
OL,6,FCo-accused Clair Malik, 43, of the
OL,7,Fsame address pleaded guilty to one
OL,8,Fcharge of failing to meet Boomer's
OL,9,Fneeds in relation to his weight.
OL,11,FShe was banned from keeping dogs for
OL,12,Ffive years, fined #120 and ordered to
OL,13,Fpay #400 costs and a #40 victim
OL,14,Fsurcharge.
OL,16,FRSPCA Inspector Kim Walters, who
OL,17,Finvestigated for the charity, said:
OL,18,F"Animals feel pain and suffering just
OL,19,Flike we do and always deserve to be
OL,20,Fshown kindness and compassion.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
