CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783678767
OL,3,CMan banned from keeping animals after
OL,4,Che was filmed throwing dog over gate
OL,6,F"We're so grateful to everyone who
OL,7,Fspeaks up for animals and grateful to
OL,8,Fthe neighbour for reporting what
OL,9,Fthey'd witnessed.
OL,11,F"We will always look into reports of
OL,12,Fanimals suffering, and we depend on
OL,13,Fthe public to be our eyes and ears and
OL,14,Freport any concerns to us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@[O]
